            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3a0014-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-30T23:52:44.163+09:00">安于上天的安排，知道自己命运所在，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-30T23:52:54.1+09:00">我有什么可担忧的呢？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-30T23:53:56.332+09:00">【二言：指前后说法不一致。】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-3a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-30T23:55:06.98+09:00">【迹：指表象。】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-30T23:56:49.939+09:00">懂得道的人不觉得它们有什么不同。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:03:53.699+09:00">这句话意为：”迹”和"心”都没有违背"一"（即把一切都纳人怀中的道）。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-4a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:05:51.861+09:00">【这段话讲的其实是"道”。魏征问王通：圣人也有忧虑担心吗？王通说:普天之下，人们都在担忧，我能无所忧虑吗？魏征又问心中存有疑惑的事情。王通答：所有人心中都有疑惑，我能幸免吗？魏征退下后，王通告诉董常：安于上天的安排，知道自己命运所在，我有什么可担忧的呢？知晓事物最根本的道理，了解事物最根本的性质，我有什么可疑虑的呢？董常对老师说:您说的跟刚才讲给魏征的不一样，为何前后不一致呢？王通解释道：魏征所问的关乎"迹”--表象，我告诉你的关乎"心”--根本；表象和根本判然有别，所以我才前后说法不一致。董常继续问："心”与“迹”的确不同吗？王通说:从你的角度看，当然是不同的。但对于懂得道（原文中的“造”就是道）的人来说，他们不会觉得二者有什么不同，表象和根本各归其所，都没有违背"一”--把一切都纳入怀中的道。　　王通弟弟王绩的一位叫做李播的朋友听到后，感叹道："一”真是伟大啊！万事万物在不知不觉中归于道。王通在这段话里，显然认为魏征只能懂得表象而无法深入根本。就学问而言，董常之于王《文中子》通说 89通，一如颜回之于孔子。所以，王通对董常的讲解要深刻得多。】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-4a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:31:41.069+09:00">【万事万物在不知不觉中归于道.】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-5a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:32:42.288+09:00">「志”就是要成就圣王明君之道；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-5a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:32:45+09:00">文字则用来宣讲这种志向.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-5a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:33:19.149+09:00">在"诏”（帝王使用的文体之一）中，可以看到君王的志向：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-5a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:33:47.992+09:00">体恤人民要周到，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-5a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:34:14.857+09:00">满足人民的需要要完备.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-5a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:34:23.811+09:00">说出的话，全国来响应:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-5a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:34:24.258+09:00">发出的命令，不会轻易被改变。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-5a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:35:13.985+09:00">有仁爱之心和智慧，博学多识，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-5a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:35:52.968+09:00">通达事理,并且以上天为法则，知道命运之所在。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-6a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:38:24.317+09:00">应用广泛，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:38:24.38+09:00">在"策”中，语言典雅，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-6a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:38:27.47+09:00">对人民有所怜悯，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-6a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:39:21.772+09:00">君王不知疲劳.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:43:58.796+09:00">【①《命》：学者张沛认为这是《续书》中的一篇。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:45:07.903+09:00">其中提到了君臣</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:45:08.331+09:00">根据某地实际情况推行治理的情况。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:46:34.268+09:00">其中提到了国家成败</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:46:30.332+09:00">从而不得不去做的情况。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:46:35.686+09:00">全在此，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:48:32.619+09:00">它不会抛弃任何东西，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:48:33.235+09:00">都应当与合适的时机相契合。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:48:33.475+09:00">治国之道太广大了，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:48:33.836+09:00">其中还提到了（对国家治理的）消长变化，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:48:39.445+09:00">不受任何约束而独自运行，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:48:48.13+09:00">合乎情势所需，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-7a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T00:49:12.552+09:00">成就自己的天命。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:01:43.381+09:00">做事情，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:03:07.78+09:00">要根据仁义的原则并进行谋划。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:03:54.049+09:00">为什么要有常设的老师呢？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:04:27.772+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:04:34.088+09:00">只有贤明的君主</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:05:28.976+09:00">完成事关天下的大业；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:05:47.238+09:00">接受有关治理天下的训诫，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:05:52.996+09:00">明了治理天下的根本道理，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:06:02.134+09:00">可以依据道的标准，以一个天下统治者的身份，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:06:07.417+09:00">在这一过程中，人民并不知道</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-8a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:09:14.182+09:00">君；主在努力作为。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-9a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:41:48.944+09:00">根据具体的情况，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-9a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:42:49.662+09:00">容选择合适的内。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-9a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:43:23.464+09:00">晁错、董仲舒和公孙弘三人写给皇上的对策，洋洋洒洒.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-9a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T03:08:41.171+09:00">通达事理的大臣可以有针对性的回答。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-9a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T01:45:13.546+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-10a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:26:36.065+09:00">把美好的东西藏而不宣，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-10a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:27:53.828+09:00">天下人怎么会知道什么是美好呢？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-10a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:28:42.685+09:00">称赞其美德.纠正其错误。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-10a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:29:21.661+09:00">不停地向善的境界迈进。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-11a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:30:15.243+09:00">开放人民议政，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-11a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:30:41.246+09:00">天下人内心的想法就都可以知道了.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-11a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:32:42.814+09:00">②合宫：传说中黄帝听政议政的地放。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-11a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:35:05.955+09:00">把全天下人的谋略汇集起来，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-11a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:36:38.652+09:00">把全天下人的聪明才智集合起来，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-11a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:37:33.295+09:00">这样就能获得最根本的道理了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-12a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:46:44.327+09:00">人心中总是充满险恶，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-12a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:47:12.62+09:00">道德之心总是微弱，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-12a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T04:47:32.946+09:00">这说的是"道”很难有进展。【这里提出了"人心"与"道心”的对立，对后世的理学有启迪。】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-12a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:00:50.462+09:00">自己虽然正确但不当面指责他人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-12a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:01:03.645+09:00">辛劳但是不发出埋怨，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-12a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:01:18.048+09:00">风格委婉但不去谄媚，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-12a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:01:26.309+09:00">性格耿直但是讲究礼数。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:40:11.853+09:00">不怕改错、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-13a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:40:15.844+09:00">不去谴责他人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-13a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:40:55.67+09:00">这样的人擅长弥补过失。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-13a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:42:00.041+09:00">尽忠补过：尽其忠心.帮助君王改正错误。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:42:39.803+09:00">把灾难变成吉祥，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:44:29.364+09:00">让贤明替代昏聵。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-16a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:48:56.152+09:00">【太和之政：指北魏孝文帝推行的一系列政策。】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-19a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:52:25.047+09:00">在"制"、“命”（二者都是王通作品《续书》中的内容，"志”、-事''同）中，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-19a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:52:31.8+09:00">有人物的为人之道；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-19a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:52:34.266+09:00">在“志”、“事"中说的是人物有所克制。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-20a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:54:15.536+09:00">意为：一心一意，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-20a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:54:46.975+09:00">恪守中道。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-20a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:55:16.371+09:00">无以下体:不采摘植物的根茎，有所节制。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-21a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:56:45.759+09:00">“事”对于"命”，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-21a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:56:47.112+09:00">就像有"志”就有”制”。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-22a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:57:29.29+09:00">知晓了"制"、"命”中缜含的道理，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-22a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T05:58:08.073+09:00">就理解王公贵族的所作所为了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-22a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T06:00:19.996+09:00">变化之心：变化的根本.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-22a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T06:00:55.316+09:00">知晓了"志"、"事"中蕴含的道理，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-22a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-31T06:01:25.013+09:00">就理解君臣之间的难处在哪里了.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T00:53:02.193+09:00">王通祖父王杰的一部著作.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-25a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T01:16:00.959+09:00">做错了事情而不知反省，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-25a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T01:16:01.736+09:00">这就完了.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-30a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T01:43:12.102+09:00">比照天道，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-30a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T01:43:16.894+09:00">与人道契合，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-30a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T01:43:28.343+09:00">在这里有定数，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-30a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T01:43:37.873+09:00">在那里有感应，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-30a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T01:43:37.892+09:00">这就是“命，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-30a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T01:45:44.062+09:00">知而畏之：知命而有敬艮之心。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-30a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T01:45:56.144+09:00">至之：成就天命。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_005-31a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T01:51:33.15+09:00">薛收问老师什么是“命"。王通的回答是：比照天道，与人道契合，在这里有定数，在那里有感应，这就是"命”。他认为：人生当中的吉凶顺利，都是命定，个体无法逃避；只有有德行的人，才能知命而有敬畏之心；只有圣人，才可以成就天命。薛收接着问：古人有一本属于《易经》类的著作《元命》，它能讲清楚天命吗？王通给了肯定的回答。这里的"元命”也可能就是天命，对其的理解有分歧。王通的重点在于让弟子常怀敬畏之心来对待早有命定的事情；人有了敬畏之心，在现实中就不会肆意妄为。p.75】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-15a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-01T02:02:49.419+09:00">【薛收这里所问关乎"天人”。他问王通仲长子光是什么样的人。王通说:一位“天人”。仲长子光是一位和王通家熟识的人，王通的弟弟王绩与他志气相投。《新唐书》王绩的传里，提到过他："仲长子光者，亦隐者也,无妻子，结庐北渚，凡三十年,非其力不食”（《新唐书》列传121）。从中可知，这位子光先生是一位隐士，没有家庭，自食其力。王通对隐者都很客气。他把仲长子光称为"天人”。薛收于是想让老师解释"天人”的含义。王通答道：形体是渺小的，从这点看，仲长子光是一个人;然而思想是博大深远的，所以他成就了自己的天性。这样的人，就是"天人"---------个有天性的个体。薛收问："圣人与天地如何？"子曰："天生之，地长之，圣人成之。故天地立而《易》行乎其中矣。"（《魏相篇》）薛收问到了“圣人。” p. 76】</seg>
